除左用鬥黃進行分化，仲用扮演移民/留守派黎進行分化</span>，大家請保持獨立思考<br />\n<br />\n借個位<br />\n連登一向錯曬風向，<span style=\"color: red;\">英國點日落都好，香港問題上都係重要持分者</span>，必須engage。<br />\n我地唔係要拉攏政府班奶共狗（例如Dominic Rabb），而係要<span style=\"color: red;\">拉攏英國民意</span>啊。英國係民主國家，民意最重要。英國民意決定stand with Hong Kong/Boycott China，BJ以至成個政府都無得唔跟。<span style=\"color: red;\">宜家武肺英國死左就三萬幾人，正是推動報仇民意好機會</span>。<br />\n<br />\n另外要借助美國向英國施壓，因為<span style=\"color: red;\">美國有動機（報武肺之仇）同拳頭，加英國有理由（聯合聲明），兩個加埋先容易嚮香港問題做野</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">最後大家要幫手簽個聯署支持BNO平權救手足</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.change.org/p/uk-govt-uk-govt-introduce-alistair-carmichael-s-private-members-bill-on-hong-kong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.change.org%2Fp%2Fuk-govt-uk-govt-introduce-alistair-carmichael-s-private-members-bill-on-hong-kong&d=tjA1itiRAyOaH4WNB6QjYxTmJET03dBbukdTSFliYCA%3D&h=9c1f337c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.change.org/p/uk-govt-uk-govt-introduce-alistair-carmichael-s-private-members-bill-on-hong-kong</a>"},{"pid":"0645629cf03c4924804cbc56e26b4de398f22df2","tid":2035112,"uid":140953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d904392873a31f346a9dbc2e4f8fe93f08fb1c14","tid":2035112,"uid":265980,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"520aec23a4378ae29a59b26f1426e8111e2d3323","tid":2035112,"uid":140953,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T16:26:37.000Z","msg":"講就好多<br />\n之前去旅行10個後生仔可能得1個係用BNO<br />\n去日本韓國買野退稅d人都好驚訝你係英國人，證明唔多香港人用"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T16:54:03.000Z","msg":"邊有驚訝 我一直都用bno<br />\n日本韓國都冇野<br />\n其實宜家大把人有其他國家護照<br />\n點會咁大驚小怪"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T17:45:19.000Z","msg":"韓國日本西方遊客唔係想像中咁多，尤其係英國人<br />\n通常可能英國人唔會好似香港人咁買藥妝買衫買得咁痴線<br />\n自然少接觸英國護照"},{"pid":"eed4f5d7f2042aa86685b6f46a60a2230750f3f1","tid":2035112,"uid":2646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T23:30:39.000Z","msg":"咁多人有"},{"pid":"